{"tid":2489583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發 董健華進場時一瘸一拐  離場要兩人攙扶下台","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T04:56:08.000Z","uid":5195,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"26698aa96809eeef2282fbb3dbc3a52a19636e15","tid":2489583,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme4nPjqSQeiUb6idaAMgRa1Y6b6VU4cWGfYQ2UxnCknRp?filename=bcDOoPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcDOoPQ.jpg&h=36d3c5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年83歲、上月於全國人大會議開幕式上跌倒的全國政協副主席董健華亦有到場，惟他進場時一瘸一拐，離場時更須駐港國安公署署長鄭雁雄及中聯辦主任駱惠寧攙扶下台。記者追問其身體狀況時，他未有回應便離去。<br />\n<br />\n董建華3月5日於北京出席全國人大會議開幕式，離場時失足跌倒在地。當時董建華由他人扶起，隨後自行步行離開會議廳，行政長官林鄭月娥及全國政協副主席梁振英亦上前關心及慰問。"},{"pid":"effe076319c7cccf1958a749bc07079dec38098c","tid":2489583,"uid":31237,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"幾時死？"},{"pid":"515363fbaa905434e296d5f6e14d04af4d3d7c83","tid":2489583,"uid":126283,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"打完第二針？"},{"pid":"b30866a03825241697a654f500a94d9c2fab9813","tid":2489583,"uid":56123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"毛主席召見"},{"pid":"aad17bfbaa9f6eec5df3c9786032d0796bb18981","tid":2489583,"uid":69125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"腳痛咗咁多年?"},{"pid":"f428b43bdcdfb341872fe282608d6e02785d9e40","tid":2489583,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"好快拉柴"},{"pid":"879375d5ce58c6bb7f26538ec08486cd78c1dd9c","tid":2489583,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"國家領導人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/dcd9db